appointments
  should display an appointment's doctor (FAILED - 1)
  should display an appointment's patient (FAILED - 2)
  should display an appointment's date and time (FAILED - 3)
  should not have an index page (FAILED - 4)

doctors
  #show page
    shows all of a doctor's appointment times in a human readable format (FAILED - 5)
    links to the patient's show page by name for each appointment (FAILED - 6)

patients
  #index page
    lists all of the patients and the number of appointments they have (FAILED - 7)
  #show page
    shows all of a patient's appointment times in a human readable format (FAILED - 8)
    links to the doctor's show page by name for the doctor of each appointment (FAILED - 9)

Appointment
  has a date and time (FAILED - 10)
  belongs to a patient (FAILED - 11)
  belongs to a doctor (FAILED - 12)

Doctor
  has a name (FAILED - 13)
  has a department (FAILED - 14)
  has many appointments (FAILED - 15)
  has many patients, through appointments (FAILED - 16)

Patient
  has a name (FAILED - 17)
  has an age (FAILED - 18)
  has many appointments (FAILED - 19)
  has many doctors, through appointments (FAILED - 20)